            612 + 4 * 414 + 193 - (4 * 414 + 348 + 2 * 276)
            = -95 ~= -100 kJ/mol
        iv?
            This is because there are stronger bonds between the atoms in the product than between the atoms in the reactants. This results in a negative molar enthalpy change, which means the reaction is exothermic.
